        <header>
            
                <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr "
                    data-isverify="False"
                    data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/3683898/new_review">
                    <span>我要写书评</span>
                </a>
            <h2>
                    向日葵不开的夏天的书评 · · · · · ·

                    <span class="pl">( <a href="reviews">全部 234 条</a> )</span>
            </h2>
        </header>
        
            
            <div class="review_filter">
                            <a href="javascript:;;" class="cur" data-sort="">热门</a>
                            <a href="javascript:;;" data-sort="time">最新</a>
                            <a href="javascript:;;" data-sort="follow">好友</a>
                        <a href="/subject/3683898/reviews?version=1" data-sort="version">只看本版本的评论</a>
            </div>
            <script>
                var cur_sort = '';
                $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter a').on('click', function () {
                    var sort = $(this).data('sort');
                    if(sort === cur_sort) return;

                    if(sort === 'follow' && true){
                        window.location.href = '//www.douban.com/accounts/login?source=movie';
                        return;
                    }

                    if($('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing')) return;
                    $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing', true);

                    cur_sort = sort;

                    $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter a').removeClass('cur');
                    $(this).addClass('cur');

                    $.getJSON('reviews', { sort: sort }, function(res) {
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review-list').remove();
                        $('#reviews-wrapper [href="reviews?sort=follow"]').parent().remove();
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').after(res.html);
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').data('doing', false);
                        $('#reviews-wrapper .review_filter').removeData('doing');

                        if (res.count === 0) {
                            $('#reviews-wrapper .review-list').html('<span class="no-review">你关注的人还没写过长评</span>');
                        }
                    });
                });
            </script>


            



<div class="review-list  ">
        
    

            
    
    <div data-cid="4659671">
        <div class="main review-item" id="4659671">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jinyiye/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2216709-38.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jinyiye/" class="name">星X</a>

            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2011-02-20" class="main-meta">2011-02-20 23:53:52</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4659671/">个人关于《向日葵》的最终解读（主题，谜题，故事） 严重剧透。</a></h2>

                <div id="review_4659671_short" class="review-short" data-rid="4659671">
                    <div class="short-content">
                            <p class="spoiler-tip">这篇书评可能有关键情节透露</p>

                        我看过的推理小说虽然不多，但也有十几本了，《向日葵》不是我看过的最好的，却是最让我有倾诉欲望的小说——夏天、青春、诡异、崩坏、阴暗的少年——尤其是当我看到道夫杀死s君，喂给美香时，真是如同被雷击了一样从头到脚的震撼。 总而言之，如果你是个传统的，保守的，死硬...

